Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=24}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao Smoker! Noticias terriveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma mensagem do quartel-general!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:06.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy e sua tripulacao\Nestao vindo pra ca, pra Loguetown!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:10.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele acabou de receber uma recompensa\Nde 30 milhoes de belly no East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:14.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma recompensa de 30 milhoes...\NParabens pra ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:18.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ele e tao perigoso que ate derrubou\No Don Krieg e o tritao Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Silencio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa sua gritaria\Nfez tudo desmontar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao e bom deixar\Nas coisas te estressarem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu acho melhor fazer as coisas\Nno seu proprio ritmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao concorda?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:44.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao, do que se trata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso! E sobre um grupo de piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi informado que eles podem\Naparecer na cidade hoje... Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que tao estressado?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Algum pirata conseguiu\Nescapar dessa cidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:58.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,desde que eu assumi o comando?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nao, senhor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao se acalme de uma vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce vai estragar meu ritmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:09.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Informando, senhor! Temos noticias\Nde que piratas chegaram ao porto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, va ate la imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deve ser a tripulacao do Luffy!\NEles chegaram na cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:19.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Trinta milhoes, hein...? Espero que\Nele pelo menos de algum trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:20.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Senhor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So falando sozinho. Esquece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:26.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao quer olhar isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.27,Note-207-,,0,0,0,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao! Por favor de\Nas ordens a cada unidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:34.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao precisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas ele pode acabar\Nsendo bem forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esquece isso. Onde ta a Tashigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim. Ela mencionou que\Nestaria ocupada de manha,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:47.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas que viria pro treinamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:50.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquela garota desastrada.\NPra onde ela foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eba! Um sorvete de tres bolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Devagar!\NVoce vai derrubar se correr!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Capitao Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Meu sorvete...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:09.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Eu sinto muito pela minha filha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa! Desculpa!\NDesculpa! Desculpa! Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:18.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa ai.\NMinhas calcas comeram seu sorvete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Toma, compra cinco bolas pra voce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:22.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:36.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saqueia tudo! Nao deixa\Nnem uma batata pra tras!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:43.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Eu, o futuro Rei dos Piratas Gally, o Crescente,\Nvou precisar desses suprimentos na minha viagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entreguem tudo com gratidao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem e o responsavel aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que {\i1}voce{\i0} quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao voce e o Monkey D. Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:05:00.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero te testar pra ver se voce\Ne digno de pisar na minha cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que monte de besteira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pega ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitao Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim. Ele era um dos caras mais\Nduros do Quartel-General da Marinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:23.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa cidade costumava ser um ponto\Nde encontro dos piratas a caminho da Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:28.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas desde que ele assumiu o comando,\Ntodo pirata que veio pra cidade
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,acabou atras das grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A forca dele e extraordinaria.\NEle e um monstro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:38.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dizem ate que ele tem\Npoderes de fruta do diabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Poderes de fruta do diabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incrivel, Capitao! Voce capturou\Na tripulacao do Luffy num instante!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:54.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seus olhos sao so de enfeite?\NEsse cara obviamente nao e o Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O mundo ia acabar antes\Ndesse cara valer 30 milhoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Entao, onde ta o Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele vai aparecer em breve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A diversao ta so comecando.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:12.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E agora eu to no porto.\NComo eu vim parar aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele e um desses caras?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao tenho certeza. Provavelmente nao...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:22.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Na hora certa! Voce sabe como\Nchegar na plataforma de execucao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Plataforma de execucao...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu me perdi no caminho...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca te vi\Npor aqui antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:30.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim! Eu acabei de chegar nessa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:34.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa cidade e enorme mesmo! E bem\Ndiferente da Vila do Moinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E por que a plataforma de execucao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero ver o lugar onde\No Rei dos Piratas morreu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao voce nao sabe onde e? Bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera. Segue a fumaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah! E por ali?! Valeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que droga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:17.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Eu achava que tava indo pra plataforma\Nde execucao, mas aqui nao pode ser o lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:20.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, tanto faz. Eu chego la uma hora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E por aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gold... Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce trabalha aqui, velhote?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tava escrito "Gold Roger"\Nna placa la fora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse e o nome do lugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cai fora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui nao e lugar pra um pirralho como voce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:06.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alem disso, a gente ta fechando de vez hoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce ta falindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:11.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A gente nao ta falindo!\NEu mesmo to fechando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora some daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu so fiquei curioso com o nome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu to um pouco perdido.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu to tentando chegar\Nna plataforma de execucao...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce pode me dizer como chegar la?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que e isso na mesa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um cranio?! E enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:34.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso e o que sobrou de um cara\Nque chamavam de Gigante Assassino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:39.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele era um demonio que mandou centenas\Nde piratas pro outro mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:45.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas Gold Roger mandou {\i1}ele{\i0} pro\Noutro mundo com um unico golpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Gold Roger fez isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com uma velocidade relampago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse e o ferimento que ele recebeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O homem pode ter vivido de forma horrivel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas com seu ultimo suspiro, ele murmurou,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Roger... Tiro meu chapeu pra voce...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que voce seja eternamente\Nhonrado entre os piratas."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Demais! Que massa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:12.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando eu ouvi que ele tinha conquistado\Na Grand Line um pouco depois,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:16.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A felicidade superou minha surpresa,\Ne minha empolgacao desmentiu minha idade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:24.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}E entao, ha vinte e dois anos atras, hoje,\NRoger morreu na plataforma de execucao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:30.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}E desde aquele dia, todo novato metido\Nentrou de cabeca na pirataria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi o comeco\Nda Grande Era dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas olha o que aconteceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:40.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa cidade ta cheia de nada\Nalem de covardes e escoria agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:45.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Homens loucos o bastante pra desafiar\Nesse mar maligno praticamente sumiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:49.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E por isso que esse bar\Nta fechando de vez hoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tambem vou pra Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Gold Roger e tao legal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele e como um pirata deveria ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E por isso que eu sai pro mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:03.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou pra Grand Line,\Nvou pegar o One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e me tornar o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sao palavras bem grandes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E logo nesse bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu so disse o que eu quis dizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Garoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:26.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Se ainda tem clientes como voce por ai,\Ntalvez eu segure um pouco antes de fechar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como e que eu vou saber se tem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boa! Claro que\Nvoce nao saberia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao ficava de bom humor\Nassim desde aquela epoca...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu te pago uma bebida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao bebo alcool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo! Tenho a coisa certa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:47.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer um brinde!\NAo eterno Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ao eterno Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:09.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incrivel! Isso e\Num atum gigante elefante!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:13.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo! Provavelmente veio\Nmisturado do oceano sul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu pesquei com vara e linha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com vara e linha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um atum gigante elefante...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo, entao, levem embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Certo!\N– Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Espera um segundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:25.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quanto custa?! Deixa eu comprar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu comprei bastante, bastante mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:36.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora meus preparativos pra ser um bravo\Nguerreiro do mar estao completos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So falta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:43.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, e! Esqueci a coisa mais\Nimportante. Oculos de protecao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:47.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Os melhores oculos pro melhor atirador!\NTem algo mais basico que isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao economizando nos\Nmelhores oculos por ai
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:54.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e a essencia de ser\No melhor atirador!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oculos! Oculos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses aqui! Esses oculos!\NSao simplesmente perfeitos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:10.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dona!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:14.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce tem bom olho! Sao\No modelo mais recente do North Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:18.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu peguei de um navio de importacao que\Nso sai da Marinha uma vez por ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual o problema? Sem dinheiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu so trabalho com dinheiro vivo,\Nentao, vai ser o que?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nao, e que... Ah!\NIsso! Minha mochila...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu levo esses oculos, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nossa! Que menininha mais fofa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim, sim, sim! Voce tem sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:35.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse e o unico par na cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vi eles primeiro, entao–
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:42.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sai fora, velhote!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,V...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Velhote?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para! Para ai, voce!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escuta! Antes de mais nada!\NEu nao sou velhote de jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:59.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou mais como um irmao mais velho. Entendeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?! Do que voce\Nta falando, velhote?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga, voce falou de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:05.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So me da logo esses oculos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:05.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ta com algum problema?! Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Continua reclamando\Ne eu chamo a Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:12.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:16.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso! Eu sou amigo de um\Ncapitao da Marinha nessa cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O velhao da fumaca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.75,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Quem e essa garota?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao sabe quem eu sou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:27.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o grande Capitao Usopp!\NEu destrui os Piratas Tritoes do Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi uma batalha mortal! Os tritoes me\Ncercaram 200—nao, 300 contra 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:35.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sozinho, eu soquei, joguei, pisoteei,\Nchutei e acabei com todos eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:40.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gracas a isso, agora eu tenho uma\Nrecompensa de 30 milhoes de belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendo. 30 milhoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso! E isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa?! Agora voce ta me chamando de Pa–
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:49.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui esta um presente pra voce, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Feliz aniversario!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, Carol...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:04.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que anjinha atenciosa\Nque voce e! Te amo, Carol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eu te amo, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.13,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Que familia e essa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:15.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas escuta! Aquele velhote sacana ali\Nta tentando roubar seu presente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:19.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Calma, calma! "Sacana" e palavra feia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce devia ter educacao, ta?
Comment: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:27.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por acaso voce esta implicando\Ncom a minha adoravel Carol?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-I-Implicando...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao e so isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:38.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce tem uma recompensa de\N30 milhoes de belly, eu ouvi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deixa eu ver aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses sao os novos cartazes de procurado?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu peguei eles\Ndo posto agora mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seiscentos mil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um milhao e trezentos mil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Setecentos mil... Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Trinta milhoes... Chapeu de Palha Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:57.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra uma primeira recompensa ser tao alta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:59.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera ai, garoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-S-Sim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao, veja bem, senhor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:07.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu obviamente nao sou a pessoa\Nno cartaz! Eu tava so mentindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:10.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Minha brincadeirinha boba foi\Num sucesso! Bom, tchau!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse e voce, nao e?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-I-Isso mesmo!\NCom certeza! Sou eu sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas saiba de uma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:22.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se voce encostar um dedo em mim,\Nmeu capitao Luffy nao vai ficar quieto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:26.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele e um homem mau,\Nsanguinario e diabolico!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ninguem nunca cruzou o caminho dele\Ne viveu pra contar a historia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:33.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce tem uma filha, entao devia\Ndar mais valor a sua vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendo. Nao parece valer a pena.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:42.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma recompensa de 30 milhoes deixa claro\Nque esse tal de Luffy nao e um homem comum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa! Voce e obviamente muito mais forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e o mais forte do mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Carol, ta tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:53.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Contanto que eu ganhe o suficiente\Npra nos sustentar, eu to feliz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:56.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e muito mais importante pra mim\Ndo que ser o melhor do mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.81,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele ta recuando mesmo\Ndepois de tudo que eu disse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.52,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Otimo! Nesse caso...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao voce percebeu o quanto eu sou assustador?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Segue meu conselho! So entrega\Nesses oculos pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:16.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao se preocupe! Eu pago por eles!\NEntao so me da aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:20.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que diabos voce disse isso\Nquando ele tava prestes a te deixar–
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:21.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:22.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao vamos resolver isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:26.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu suponho que voce nao tem problema\Nem resolver isso numa luta justa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma luta...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:32.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma luta...?! V-Voce nao ta\Nfalando de um duelo, ne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se voce ganhar, os oculos sao seus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:40.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma, duas, tres, quatro,\Ncinco, seis... {\i1}trinta{\i0} pistolas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nao me diga que voce e...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Daddy, o Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um duelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai ter um duelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E um duelo com o Daddy the Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele disse Daddy the Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:56.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Daddy the Father e o maior\Ncacador de recompensas pistoleiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo no East Blue sabe disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:03.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que tipo de idiota\Ndesafiaria ele pra um duelo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, desse tipo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte, narigudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:13.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao se preocupe se ele te derrotar!\NJa cavamos sua cova!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:19.39,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Como as coisas chegaram nesse ponto?\NO que ha de errado comigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As regras sao simples. Nos dois andamos\Ndez passos e depois viramos e atiramos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que voce ta fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:25.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:29.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enfrentando o Daddy the Father num\Nduelo... Voce perdeu o juizo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Cala a boca! So aconteceu,\Nentao cala a boca e assiste!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce tem um tiro. Ta pronto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.24,Main-207-,,0,110,0,,{\an3}Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.24,Main-207-,,110,0,0,,{\an1}Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tres!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quatro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cinco!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.59,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso ta feio... Muito feio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.68,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao tem como eu conseguir\Nganhar do Daddy the Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:02.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:07.69,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou morrer aqui?!\NIsso nao pode ta acontecendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:08.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sete!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.70,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu acabei de comecar minha aventura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.99,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda nem ganhei nenhuma coragem\Nou masculinidade ou nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:18.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Falou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e demais, Papa! Voce e muito legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cara, que patetico.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que duelo ridiculo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:48.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu achava que ele teria mais coragem\Nque isso. Que decepcionante.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem voce pensa\Nque e, tentando trapacear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:55.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu covarde fracote!\NVoce nao pode pelo menos lutar honestamente?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:59.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Eu sinto muito! Me perdoa!\NEu sou so um homem baixo e patetico!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:02.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao ganharia nada\Nmatando alguem como eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo?! Certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao pode simplesmente me deixar ir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:13.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-Isso! Se e dinheiro\Nque voce quer, ela tem bastante!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So por favor nao atira em mim!\NPor favor, poupe minha vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora voce ta se escondendo atras de uma mulher?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:22.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enfim–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao! Esquece o que eu disse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela e uma inocente que nao tem nada a ver com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:31.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso arrastar ela pra isso,\Nmesmo que eu leve um tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor! Eu te imploro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"Usopp..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Garoto, seu nome e Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:46.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce conhece um homem chamado\NYasopp dos Piratas do Ruivo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:49.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yasopp? Esse e o nome do meu pai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,V-Voce ja conheceu meu pai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao voce {\i1}e{\i0} o filho dele...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:03.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca contei pra ninguem\No que aconteceu naquele dia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas vou abrir uma excecao.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:11.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aconteceu numa cidade portuaria\Nquente e seca, parecida com essa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:15.48,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos la, Subtenente Masterson!\NCada um tem um tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:19.07,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Um! Dois! Tres!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:37.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me mata! Agora que perdi um duelo,\Nnao tenho razao pra viver...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que voce ta fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sua filha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me devolve...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:50.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um subtenente da Marinha, guardando\Nalgo assim com tanto cuidado...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce deve mimar muito ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:54.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao me de licao, seu pirata imundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por mim tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce foi otimo, Yasopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao foi nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse ferimento mostra\Nminha inexperiencia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas voce enfrentou o Daddy Masterson!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce ganhou porque e voce!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:11.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E, a gente nunca teria\Nchance nenhuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Valeu, Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:18.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agradeco por ter assistido\Nao duelo sem dizer nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso que e bom!\NQuer um pouco, Subtenente?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Familia, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:34.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ter familia nao e tao ruim.\NMas eu nao levo jeito pra isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:35.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:39.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho um filho.\NO nome dele e Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:40.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Faz anos que nao vejo ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:44.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sai pro mar quando\Nele ainda era bem pequeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:48.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que? Voce nao ama seu filho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao era sobre isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era a bandeira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ouvi o chamado da bandeira pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso ai, Yasopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao ha nada que eu possa fazer pelo meu filho.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:15.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ate um pai sem esperanca\Ncomo eu ja e demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fique sempre ao lado da sua filha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao pode deixar ela se sentir sozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Embora eu nao tenha moral pra falar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:32.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu perdi nosso duelo! Yasopp! Acaba comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:35.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao me de sua piedade miseravel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:36.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esquece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:40.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voces da Marinha podem nos enforcar\Nno momento que nos pegarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:44.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas nos piratas somos livres pra matar\Nou poupar quem a gente quiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:45.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ate mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:03.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa! Voce perdeu pra um pirata,\Ne ele poupou sua vida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:08.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas isso e incrivel!\NSeu pai deve ser muito habilidoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.67,0:23:09.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:11.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Normalmente voce...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:14.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Normalmente voce contaria\Npra um garoto patetico como eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:16.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,uma historia vergonhosa\Nsobre ter sua vida poupada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:22.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce me contou isso pra me dar coragem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:25.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A maioria das pessoas teria vergonha\Ndemais de contar uma historia assim,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:28.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas voce contou mesmo sabendo\Nque ia ficar muito menos legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:33.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Independente de quao corajoso\Nvoce mostrou que meu pai e. Certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nenhum fracote ou covarde\Nconseguiria fazer o que voce fez!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:41.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Carol! Seu pai e\No homem mais corajoso do mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:43.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce pode encontrar caras fortes em qualquer lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.95,0:23:48.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas eu nunca vi um homem tao\Nforte e gentil quanto seu pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:57.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu... Eu nao posso desistir! Tenho que\Nser corajoso, ou vou envergonhar seu pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:23:59.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Me da uma chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:02.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me enfrenta em outro duelo de vida ou morte!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:03.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao vou trapacear dessa vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:12.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem. Esse vai ser\Nnosso duelo de verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:15.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Escolha a arma com a qual\Nvoce se sente mais confortavel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:21.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bom. Agora, entao. Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:27.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tente acertar aquele catavento.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.74,0:24:29.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele catavento? La em cima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.19,0:24:34.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se errar, e...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:37.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim! Voce pode me acertar\Nbem no coracao!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:37.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.07,0:24:42.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Minha vida ta em jogo\Nde verdade dessa vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.79,0:24:48.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao tem...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.19,0:24:51.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao tem como ele acertar\Nde tao longe com aquilo...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.23,0:25:13.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce errou!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.64,0:25:16.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao, Papa! Nao atira nele! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.75,0:25:22.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso atirar nele. O Usopp acertou\Nbem no topo do catavento!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.89,0:25:26.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ele acertou mesmo!\NBem no topo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.41,0:25:28.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.83,0:25:32.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e um excelente atirador.\NEu nao esperaria menos do filho do Yasopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.30,0:25:34.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nunca esqueca essa coragem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.30,0:25:38.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce vai ser igualzinho ao\Nseu pai um dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:43.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Va pra Grand Line.\NEu tenho certeza que o Yasopp ta la.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.87,0:25:44.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.31,0:25:49.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce e muito bom, velhote!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.51,0:25:50.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses nao sao...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:53.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ta tudo bem! Ate mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.50,0:25:54.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.57,0:25:56.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Carol, voce devia saber disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.68,0:25:58.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E falta de educacao dizer, "Ate mais!"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.91,0:26:00.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E mesmo! Desculpa, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.95,0:26:04.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou crescer e ser uma moca\Ndigna de ser sua filha!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.70,0:26:05.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entao voce me perdoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.94,0:26:09.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce ja e a moca mais\Neducada que existe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.17,0:26:10.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ser ainda mais educada!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.54,0:26:13.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que as pessoas o considerem uma vergonha,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.15,0:26:17.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ele sempre lutou\Npra proteger quem ama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.13,0:26:21.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ser um homem\Ncorajoso como o Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.17,0:26:25.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou me tornar um guerreiro de verdade\Ne ficar diante do meu pai um dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.67,0:26:29.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sei disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.97,0:26:38.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.20,0:26:41.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que bela recepcao...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.23,0:26:43.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e eu sou um cliente regular.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.83,0:26:47.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao sou a pessoa com quem\Nvoce deveria estar bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.77,0:26:50.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu so venho aqui como um cliente fiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:54.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A culpa e dos piratas que\Nsao todos covardes hoje em dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.03,0:26:59.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce teve um cliente? Que raro.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.09,0:27:03.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero um rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.85,0:27:06.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao tem bebida aqui pra voce!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.05,0:27:07.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nao seja tao frio.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.98,0:27:10.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hoje e um dia especial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.39,0:27:13.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce nao concorda?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.45,0:27:19.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso que e bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.01,0:27:25.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda consigo ver como se fosse ontem...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.73,0:27:29.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como o Roger estava no final...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.12,0:27:32.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era uma tarde umida,\Nassim como hoje...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.23,0:27:38.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com as maos algemadas, ele foi levado\Npela rua principal ate a praca
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.25,0:27:40.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,onde ficava a plataforma de execucao.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.23,0:27:43.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo assim, ele marchou\Ncomo um general triunfante.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.75,0:28:15.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Riqueza, fama, poder...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.93,0:28:20.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger obteve tudo\Nque o mundo tinha a oferecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.08,0:28:22.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo caminhando\Nem direcao a morte,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.55,0:28:25.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ele era a personificacao\Nde um rei cheio de orgulho...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.65,0:28:29.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vontades herdadas...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.31,0:28:32.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,as mares do tempo\Ne os sonhos da humanidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.83,0:28:36.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enquanto as pessoas buscarem liberdade,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.13,0:28:39.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,essas coisas jamais deixarao de existir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.01,0:28:50.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce tem alguma ultima palavra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.07,0:28:56.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce pode tirar isso?\NTa cocando que nao ta no gibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.16,0:28:57.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nao posso fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.43,0:28:59.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce acha que eu iria fugir?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.49,0:29:03.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho que to por minha conta.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.51,0:29:10.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos acabar logo com isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.73,0:29:28.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.49,0:29:31.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde voce escondeu\Ntodo o tesouro que encontrou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.87,0:29:34.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ta na Grand Line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.53,0:29:38.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voce encontrou, nao foi?!\NAquele tesouro lendario!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.58,0:29:40.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.04,0:29:42.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele grande tesouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.63,0:29:47.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.10,0:29:58.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Meu tesouro?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.69,0:30:00.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem disse que voce podia falar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.01,0:30:02.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E de voces, se conseguirem achar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.15,0:30:07.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu deixei tudo la!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.61,0:30:07.15,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Executem!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.65,0:30:44.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi assim que tudo comecou...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.63,0:30:48.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.11,0:30:51.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um novo cartaz de procurado!\NPoe num lugar visivel!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.65,0:30:55.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Capitao Smoker!\NDesculpe a intrusao, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.41,0:31:00.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,H-Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.15,0:31:02.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele chapeu de palha...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.07,0:31:05.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era o Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.61,0:31:12.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,La esta...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.17,0:31:19.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O lugar onde o maior\Npirata da historia morreu...
